  <result aggregation-status="0" type="1">
   <indicator ascending="1" measure="5">
    <baseline iso-date="2018-07-10" value="Programmatic Component of the National DRM Plan out of date; National Emergency Response Strategy with response protocols outdated;Strategy of Resilient Recovery to Disaster and Climate Change (CC)not designed." year="2018">
     <comment>
      <narrative xml:lang="EN"></narrative>
     </comment>
    </baseline>
    <period>
     <actual value="Instrument: Programmatic Component of the National DRM Plan (PNGRD) Updated.Milestone 1. Document with the initial proposal toupdate the PNGRD programmatic component. Progress of 10% of the 50% expected in 2019. Work has been carried out with 14 departmentsand two sectors (Ministry of Agriculture and Ministry of Justice), with whom the critical points to be adjusted of the programmaticcomponent have been identified. This has resulted in 26 recommendations for the Improvement Plan.Instrument: National EmergencyResponse Strategy with response protocols updated.Milestone 1. Design of 5 response protocols (hurricanes, volcanoes, floods,earthquakes and landslides). Progress of 23% compared to 33% expected in 2019. Components in which progress has been made include:Temporary Shelters, Emergency Humanitarian Aid, Search and Rescue, Water and Sanitation, and Critical Incident Management."></actual>
     <period-end iso-date="2021-07-10"></period-end>
     <period-start iso-date="2018-07-10"></period-start>
     <target value="Three risk management instruments for inter-institutional coordination of the National Disaster Risk Management System (SNGRD),designed and approved:1.	Programmatic component of the National DRM Plan (PNGRD) updated.2.	Five response protocols in theframework of the National Emergency Response Strategy updated.3.	Strategy of Resilient Recovery to Disaster and CC designed."></target>
    </period>
    <title>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">DRM instruments for inter-institutional coordination of the National DRM system, designed and approved</narrative>
    </title>
   </indicator>
   <title>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">Intermediate Results Indicator</narrative>
   </title>
  </result>
  <result aggregation-status="0" type="1">
   <indicator ascending="1" measure="5">
    <baseline iso-date="2018-07-10" value="National TA Program in DRM and CC not designed." year="2018">
     <comment>
      <narrative xml:lang="EN"></narrative>
     </comment>
    </baseline>
    <period>
     <actual value="Milestone 1. Proposed preliminary structure of the National TA Program (definition of objective and scope). Progress of 5% comparedto the 10% set for 2019. This progress corresponds to the first session held with the delegates of the Ministry of Environment andSustainable Development (MADS), Ministry of Housing, City and Territory (MVCT), DNP and National DRM Unit (UNGRD), in which thelessons learned, and milestones of the National TA Program were reviewed. Next steps include the structuring of the program; basedon the experiences gained by each of the entities.Milestone 2. Design of the National TA Program. No progress was made."></actual>
     <period-end iso-date="2021-07-10"></period-end>
     <period-start iso-date="2018-07-10"></period-start>
     <target value="National TA Program in DRM and CCA, designed, approved and implemented in 5 departments and 2 sectors."></target>
    </period>
